title: DaveBrubeck/PaulDesmond(1952,53,54)Fantasy 3-210,Fantasy 3-240
description:
It's becoming more difficult but I believe this to be a "new" Brubeck upload.

The burn log says something like......Not in AccurateRip database.......


These rips are good but there are simply no previous rips present with which to

compare them for accuracy.



The upload comprises (2) Fantasy LP's released as a single CD in 1982 (FANTASY


FCD-24727-2) and consisting of material from (10) sessions        THANKYOU!




tracks (#1-#8)      The Dave Brubeck Quartet Featuring Paul Desmond/Jazz At

                    the Black Hawk (Fantasy 3-210)




tracks (#9-14)      Brubeck and Desmond/Jazz at Storyville (Fantasy 3-240)
